# Rename Impact Checklist

## Code-Level (LSP Handles)

- [ ] **Declaration** — Where symbol is defined
- [ ] **Imports** — All import statements
- [ ] **Re-exports** — Barrel file exports (`export { X }`)
- [ ] **Direct references** — Function calls, variable usage
- [ ] **Type references** — In type annotations

## Semantic-Level (Deep Analysis)

- [ ] **Inheritance chains** — Classes extending this class
- [ ] **Method overrides** — Overridden methods in subclasses
- [ ] **Interface implementations** — Classes implementing this interface
- [ ] **Type aliases** — `type MyAlias = OriginalName`
- [ ] **Generic constraints** — `<T extends OriginalName>`
- [ ] **Discriminated unions** — `type Action = { type: 'OriginalName' }`
- [ ] **Mapped types** — `Pick<OriginalName, 'field'>`
- [ ] **Conditional types** — `T extends OriginalName ? X : Y`
- [ ] **Declaration merging** — Multiple interface blocks
- [ ] **Module augmentation** — Extending external types

## String-Level (Grep Required)

- [ ] **dataHooks** — `dataHooks<{ SymbolName: ... }>`
- [ ] **Translation keys** — i18n keys derived from name
- [ ] **Test descriptions** — `describe('SymbolName', ...)`
- [ ] **Test variable names** — Mock names in tests
- [ ] **Comments** — `// SymbolName does...`
- [ ] **JSDoc** — `/** @see SymbolName */`
- [ ] **Storybook** — Story titles and exports
- [ ] **CSS classes** — Classes matching component name
- [ ] **package.json** — Exports, main fields
- [ ] **webpack.config** — Aliases, entries
- [ ] **tsconfig.json** — Path mappings

## Cross-Package (If Exported)

- [ ] **External consumers** — Other packages using this
- [ ] **Re-exports** — Packages re-exporting this
- [ ] **Type-only imports** — `import type { X }`
- [ ] **SDK generation** — Generated API clients

## Validation Checklist

Before execute:
- [ ] No name collision in target scope
- [ ] No shadowing of outer scope variables
- [ ] New name is not a reserved keyword
- [ ] New name follows convention for symbol kind

After execute:
- [ ] `tsc --noEmit` passes
- [ ] All tests pass
- [ ] ESLint passes
- [ ] No orphaned old name references (grep)
